title: Hour 1 - Turds-day Night Football, Marcus Spears
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Turds-day Night Football, Marcus Spears
description:
Dan laments another terrible game on Thursday Night Football as the Washington Commanders and Chicago Bears combined for only 19 points. And former NFL DE Marcus Spears drops by to give his unfiltered thoughts on how bad the Commanders really are.
